You can also easily access and install other tools that are available in Fedora but not pre-installed (e.g. git). And create container images that snapshot all your current setup to share with others, without limits: data, source code, software versions and current libraries!

They provide ready-to-use ISO images that include pre-installed neuroscience software such as jupyter, neuron, numpy, scipy, and many more to set up a #Fedora  workstation based system. Or you can just run their ISO in a virtual machine to use it ‚Äúlive" without installation. ü§Ø
